form.text: Those who buy products and then post reviews on social media will be entered into a draw for a free gift.
Leave a review of Miri Fasion on social media and then include the URL in the comments! We'll give you a free gift if you win.
Participants during the event period will win free gifts.

- Please contact us within 7 days of receipt for returns or exchanges
   due to product defects.
- Refunds or exchanges due to a change of heart are not available.
- Items returned without notice may not be processed.
- Refunds or exchanges are unavailable for products damaged
  during storage.
- The return delivery fee for exchanges or refunds is Miri Fashion.
